Submission Commands
===============================

NOTE: These commands work on DEV ONLY!


==========================================================
BUILDER Commands
==========================================================

Command: listtable
------------------------
Description: List of the areas that you currently have in the review process
And produce a table outling who is doing what reviews. 
Syntax: listtable area <builders name>

Command:  listreview, listrev, listresponse, listresp
--------------------------------------------------------------
Description:  List all the reviews for a specific submission.
              This works for open and closed submissions.
Syntax: listreview area <request number> <review type>
  request number is the number specific to this submission.
  review type is optional, and is code, content or balance.

Command:  respondrev, resprev
--------------------------------------
Description:  Respond to a review. Should be done when actions are 
complete.
Syntax: respondrev area <request number> <review type>
  request number is the number specific to this submission.
  review type is code, content or balance

Command:  submit area
-----------------------------
Description:  This command is used to submit things for review and for the
balance group to put their review comments in a central location.  Its the
way submissions are handled, when they are approved, and who approved the
code, content and balance of the submission.

==========================================================
MENTOR Commands
==========================================================

Command:  closesub
-------------------------
Description:  This command will finalise the whole area review process. The
area should not be promoted until this has been done by the mentor..
Syntax: closesub area <request number>
request number is the number specific to this submission.


==========================================================
ARCH+ Commands
==========================================================

Command:  gotosub
------------------------
Description:  Goto the location of a Submission.
Syntax: gotosub area <request number>
request number is the number specific to this submission.

Command:  listreviews, listrevs
--------------------------------------
Description:  This command is used to list submissions in table format,
              that are being reviewed by a specified balance member.
Syntax: listreviews area <reviewer>
 reviewer is the person reviewing the submisson.

Command: listtable area
------------------------------
Description: Provides a table outline all current area submissions
and assosciated area reviewers.

Command:  lst
----------------
Description:  List a Submission.
Syntax: lst area <request number>
  request number is the number specific to this submission.

Command:  reviewsub, revsub
-------------------------------------
Description:  Review a submission for a certain review type.
Syntax: reviewsub area <request number> <review type>
  request number is the number specific to this submission.
  review type is code, content or balance.
 
==========================================================
IMP+ Commands
==========================================================

Command:  assignrev, arev
Description:  Assign a review to a specified person. Reviews MUST be at least
ARCH + 
Syntax: assignreview area <request number> <review type> <name>
  review type is code, content or balance.
  request number is the number specific to this submission.
  name is who the review will be assigned to.
  NOTE:  To assign a review to Noone use 'none'
